
==> Spring boot is built on top of Spring Framwwork

==> Spring framework is where all the hard work is done, we just use them in the spring boot

==> Spring app layers

	--> Presentation
	--> Service
	--> Persistence

					{CRUD : Create, Read, Update, Delete}


==> Repositories <===> Services 	: SERVICE LAYER
==> Services <===> Controllers		: PRESENTATION LAYER (REST API) (controllers)

